Comment.Text: Channel Selector Select the required frequency from the neural interface. Electrode - All frequencies, spectrum.
Temporal Filter We filter the frequency by time to remove unnecessary noise.
Attention and Meditation Essence technology from NeuroSky. ampling of several frequencies responsible for attention and meditation.
Simple DSP We bring huge data values to the desired values by dividing x by a certain number, different for all frequencies.
The data obtained due to delays are square, but we need to bring them to a sine wave, so we average the values.
Crop We limit the signal to 0, 127 because in midi the values are limited on these numbers.
Sgnal Merger We combine signals for joint display.
We are making the final visualization.

Lowtaco BrainSound v2.5 Built on the basis of NeuroSky TGAM. To use this script, it is best to use this particular neural interface. This scenario processes data from the EEG to Midi-understandable values, converts them to OSC. The execution of scenario is resource-intensive, since it is necessary to convert each wave to OSC separately. In version 3.0, the system will be optimized.

OSC Controllers Convert the received data into OSC information and broadcast it to the network. Default: 127.0.0.1:9001. If you want to process data on one PC and broadcast it to another, for example a laptop, you must change the address to your local laptop address, for example 192.168.1.16
Channel Rename Adding associations to the name of the channels.
Acquisition Client Receives a signal from the server.
Stream writer We write the received data to a file for further work with them.
